    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a meticulously curated specimen for the discerning pilot. This platform features a precision-mapped ECU to flatten the torque curve and a reinforced subframe engineered to neutralize lateral deflection under high-G loads. The drivetrain is exceptionally tight with zero perceptible lash, complemented by an overhauled cooling stack utilizing high-efficiency thermal management components to eliminate heat soak. Every service interval has been strictly adhered to using high-zinc synthetic lubricants to preserve valvetrain integrity. Suspension geometry has been professionally corner-balanced, significantly reducing unsprung weight for razor-sharp turn-in and telepathic feedback through the rack. This is a balanced performance ecosystem, garage-kept and strictly enthusiast-maintained. Truly a turn-key apex hunter.",
